#  This script checks whether a jss and devised(s) with the given ID string
#  are running.  If so, it prints "OK"; otherwise it prints "FAIL".

############################################################

#  $Id$

#  $Log$
#  Revision 1.7  2001/05/11 20:36:11  wenger
